- Manual live E2E re-run against the REAL blockrun.ai gateway (fresh evidence, this
  session): `wallet --action deposit --json` still mints a real, valid
  `https://pay.coinbase.com/...` link successfully — confirms the onQuote guard
  does NOT spuriously reject the real $0 quote the gateway actually returns.
